p.note:
Compensation was dealt with in the following
                        articles of the Draft Peace Treaties: Italy—article 68, paragraph 4;
                        Rumania—article 24, paragraph 4; Bulgaria—article 22, paragraph 4;
                        Hungary—article 23, paragraph 4; Finland—article 24, paragraph 4.

In the various draft treaties, the article in
                        question was numbered as follows: Italy—article 76; Rumania—article 36;
                        Bulgaria—article 34; Hungary—article 35; Finland—article 33.
